                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180401-168-off951 t18180401-168-cd952"></join>, one handkerchief, value 7s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18180401-168-victim1222" type="victimName">
                        George Alexander 
